Text.val: 13.07.2011 SH SCR16615 Changed calculation of totals (column B/C) to build
averages (based on number of month) instead of simply adding values.
04.05.2011 SH SCR16429 Changed Heller in Admin currency and repl.GB002 by GB902
-- Number of month, used to build averages for columns B/C

SQL_STMT_U.val: select CRST_MONTH from :1/CRST join :1/CLNT on :2 where CRST_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CRST_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO :3 and :4 group by CRST_MONTH for fetch only

select cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNOUTSINV) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDEBTORSACTIVE) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV91120) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV120PLUS) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINVDISPUTES) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAWAITINGFORLEGALCOLL) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNWAITINGFORLEGALCOLL) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNNODUNNINGDEBTORS) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTANODUNNINGDEBTORSFACT) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTANODUNNINGDEBTORSSPEC) as decimal(13,2)), max(CRST_DATELASTUPDATEBID710) from :1/CRST join :1/CLNT on :2 where CRST_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CRST_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO :3 and :4 for fetch only

select CRST_YEAR, CRST_MONTH, cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINVXDAYSFROINVDAT) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNOUTSINV) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNDEBTORSACTIVE) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV91120) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINV120PLUS) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAOUTSINVDISPUTES) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTAWAITINGFORLEGALCOLL) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNWAITINGFORLEGALCOLL) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTNNODUNNINGDEBTORS) as decimal(9,0)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTANODUNNINGDEBTORSFACT) as decimal(13,2)), cast(sum(CRST_TOTANODUNNINGDEBTORSSPEC) as decimal(13,2)), max(CRST_DATELASTUPDATEBID710) from :1/CRST join :1/CLNT on :2 where CRST_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CRST_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO :3 and :4 group by CRST_YEAR, CRST_MONTH order by CRST_YEAR, CRST_MONTH for fetch only
